{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位造物主 第21章 3-1 不受禁锢的未来",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "圣域龙见证过无数世界的灭亡，\\n认为人类追求可能性的心理将导致\\n灭顶之灾，因此与“起始之人”同样\\n对可能性持否定态度。面对为了避免\\n人类灭亡而袭来的圣域龙，决战一触即发。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "龙们",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你到底是什么意思，圣域龙？\\n为什么要阻止巴哈姆特复活？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "这是为了保护世界——以及人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "自“起始之人”和“起始之龙”\\n离去、由我接手管理，\\n不知已过了几度春秋。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "在此期间，\\n世界因为各种可能性\\n而分裂成了无数世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我所见过的数百、数千、数亿的\\n世界都是人类追求可能性\\n而诞生的世界——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "曾经有一个世界，那里的人把龙\\n尽数消灭。于是那里的水干涸了，\\n风停止了，大地也不再萌生新芽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "无依无靠的人类只能\\n懊悔着自己的所作所为\\n走向死亡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "也曾有过人类掌控魔力的世界。\\n人类有了能随心所欲地\\n呼风唤雨的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "然而，那个世界因为\\n微小的失误而无法停止降雨，\\n导致整个世界都沉入了大海。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "也曾有过人类与龙携手\\n共进的世界。在那个世界里，\\n人龙之间化解了矛盾。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "但结果还是形成了很多阵营，\\n彼此之间互相争斗。最终因人与人、\\n龙与龙之间的自相残杀而灭亡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "甚至也有过没有纷争的世界。\\n即使在那样的世界里，\\n人类也仍在追求新的可能性。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "人类为了追求更加充实的生活\\n而染指黑暗魔力，导致整个世界\\n被黑暗魔力所吞噬并消逝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我采取过各种各样的手段。\\n既保护甚至庇护过人类，\\n也曾强迫他们艰苦修行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "甚至也曾经认为我管理人类的\\n一举一动反而不利于他们，\\n从而选择离开他们的视线。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "然而，任何可能性的结局\\n都是相同的，世界在人类手上\\n遭到毁灭，人类也从世界上消亡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我已经无数次见证\\n世界走向这样的结局……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "看着无数次上演的光景，\\n我被迫意识到——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "靠可能性\\n是无法保护人类的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "可能性才是那味\\n毁灭人类的毒药。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可能性……怎么会是毒药……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你身为世界的管理者，\\n是想放任因“起始之人”\\n而被封闭的世界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "没错……我身为世界的管理者，\\n必须守护人类、龙……\\n以及世界上的一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "只要有可能性存在，\\n人类就不会停止探索的脚步。但是\\n“可能性的世界”的未来是一场空。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "也就是说……你虽然身为龙，\\n却要否定巴哈姆特的思想吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "“起始之龙”错了。\\n若对人类怀有慈爱之心，\\n就不该给予他们选择的余地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "愚蠢……要是否定了可能性，\\n这个世界上还剩下什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "会剩下生命——\\n无论是人、龙，\\n还是不会毁灭的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "只要活着就算是生命吗？\\n禁锢一切的牢房就叫世界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "和没经历过毁灭的人\\n说什么都是对牛弹琴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我对放弃了世界的你\\n也不想浪费口舌。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为了这个世界，你必须消失，\\n圣域龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "为了这个世界，你还是消失吧，\\n巴哈姆特的契约者。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这是演哪一出……\\n你还想袒护我不成？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我还有很多事都不懂……\\n不管是关于这个世界，\\n还是关于你的理想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "连帮助你是否正确，\\n我也还没有答案。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "那你就不要多管闲事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是，唯有一点我很清楚——\\n我也不希望可能性\\n从这个世界上消失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我不是为了帮你，\\n而是为了保卫我的\\n可能性而战，仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "随你的便……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "不管谁出手阻拦，\\n我的责任与义务都不会变。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣域龙",
            "context": "我的话就是规矩，\\n我的存在即为世界。\\n尔等——接受我的制裁吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}